          "description": "I am pleased to award four stars, as I am thoroughly impressed with the exceptional efforts of Dr. Song and his team. Their dedication to providing crucial information, which is often overlooked elsewhere, has been invaluable. The sense of community within this establishment, from the welcoming front desk staff to the diligent nurses, is truly remarkable. Furthermore, I have observed a significant improvement in the work performed on my second arm compared to the first. The recent procedure has left my skin remarkably clear and free of any visible marks, a testament to their meticulous approach.",
