          "description": "I have been a patient at American Access for well over 8 years. The entire staff is attentive and understanding. They make me feel seen and heard at this clinic. Dr Preddy and Dr.Song are some of the best physicians I have had the privilege of ever meeting. Every issue is resolved with the utmost care. The new facility although is its further from my apartment, I don\u2019t mind making the trek uptown. The new clinic is very state of the art and much larger than the location on 91street. If you are on dialysis and have a fistula, graph or catheter this is hands down the best clinic in the city to receive care. Coming here has greatly improved the outcome of my dialysis sessions, my clearance rate is 83% and I believe I owe that to care I receive at American Access to ensure my fistula is working properly. I thank the universe for the staff at American Access, they have improved my quality of life beyond what I knew was possible.",
